description:
Movement Realty is proud to present 27 Tucker Street Caboolture.
Welcome to your new home! This modern and spacious four-bedroom property is the perfect place to call home. With a large open plan living/dining area, stainless steel appliances in your kitchen, and a separate lounge with air conditioning for those hot summer days, you'll have plenty of room to entertain guests. Plus, the master bedroom includes a walk-in robe and ensuite - so you can enjoy some extra comfort in style.

And that's not all – this amazing property also includes an undercover patio area, as well as a sizeable fully fenced rear yard for any avid gardeners out there. And its convenient location means you're only minutes away from major shopping centers and cinemas, transport links, schools and all other services. So don't miss out on this incredible opportunity – come see it today!

INSIDE
- Living and dining area air conditioned
- Open kitchen with dishwasher, electric cooktop & built in pantry
- Formal lounge
- Master suite with walk in robe and ensuite
- 3 additional bedrooms all with built in robes
- Main bathroom with shower and bath

OUTDOOR
- Side access
- Water tank plumbed to house
- Security screens
- Room for a shed and/or pool (STCA)
- Fully fenced

LOCATION
- Australian Christian College 300m
- St Peters Catholic Primary School 2.15km
- Drakes supermarket, Chemist & Takeaway 500m
- Coles, Bunnings & Big Fish Tavern 3.9km
